<h3>STATUS OF GAMES</h3>

<b>DOOM and DOOM II:</b><br>
Very playable (despite the limitations listed above).

<p>
<b>Heretic:</b><br>
Close to being playable, needs more work on proper themes
(such as the Heretic style of locked doors with the statue
out front), etc...

<p>
<b>Hexen:</b><br>
Not playable just now, the map/wad building code cannot
create the Hexen-specific formats yet.

<p>
<b>Quake:</b><br>
Close to being playable, but still lacking many things: lighting,
visibility, doors, sloped floors or ceilings,
liquid areas, proper themes, etc... etc...

<p>
<b>Quake II:</b><br>
Quite far from being playable, working levels cannot be built yet,
and lacks all the same stuff missing from Quake (listed in the previous
entry).

